name: The Garden of Ephemeral Details: Eternal Ephemera #7
description: The project "The Garden of Eternal Ephemera" comprises 143 unique still frames created on the occasion of the exhibition The Garden of Earthly Delights through the artworks of Colección SOLO at Matadero, Madrid. In his installation "The Garden of Ephemeral Details" Mario Klingemann / @Quasimondo using real time AI creates a reinterpretation of The Garden of Earthly Delights by Hieronymus Bosch. Each unique NFT will reflect ephemeral details captured by the artist. This is #7.
